ass=\"text-size-medium\">We believe our people are our greatest strength. Whether you’re a future trainee an experienced solicitor, or wanting to make a difference in support you’ll find a workplace that empowers you to grow, be yourself, and make a real difference.</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" data-btn-hover=\"\" data-theme=\"primary\" href=\"/careers/current-vacancies\" class=\"btn is-icon w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">View current vacancies</p></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"impact-header_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"base\" class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">Home</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Careers</div></div></div></div></div><div grow-scroll=\"reverse\" class=\"impact-header_image-wrapper is-radius\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.05\" alt=\"Group of 15 professionally dressed adults posing indoors in front of a moss wall installation.\" loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b70ab0b4997bf0dd550b_xx.avif\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1501px) 100vw, 1501px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b70ab0b4997bf0dd550b_xx-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b70ab0b4997bf0dd550b_xx-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b70ab0b4997bf0dd550b_xx-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b70ab0b4997bf0dd550b_xx.avif 1501w\" class=\"impact-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"listing_shape-wrapper\"><div lottie=\"target-load\" class=\"header_shape is-impact\" data-w-id=\"b44880a4-d96e-f7f4-464a-54228d5b2be7\" data-animation-type=\"lottie\" data-src=\"/assets/69db9824440585a4bf466988_V_Yellow.json\" data-loop=\"0\" data-direction=\"1\" data-autoplay=\"1\" data-is-ix2-target=\"0\" data-renderer=\"svg\" data-default-duration=\"0\" data-duration=\"3\" data-loading=\"lazy\"></div></div></header><section id=\"current-vacancies\" element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_careers-v_layout-2\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"careers-v_layout-2_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid careers-v_layout-2_content\"><div class=\"careers-v_layout-2_content-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h1 class=\"heading-style-h2\">Current vacancies</h1></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Whether you’re beginning your career or taking the next step, we’ll back you with expert guidance, meaningful work, and a team that genuinely cares.</p></div><div class=\"careers-v_layout-2_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div class=\"empty-state w-dyn-empty\"><div>We don’t have any live vacancies at the moment, but we’re always interested in hearing from talented people. If that&#x27;s you, please <a href=\"/contact\">contact us</a>.<br><br>Please check back soon for future opportunities.</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_signposts\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"signposts_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid signposts_list is-3\"><div class=\"signposts_item\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-0\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Apprenticeships</h4><p>Our Apprenticeship Schemes offer a direct route to qualification as a lawyer, without the cost of university, and with support from a team known for exceptional client care</p></div></div><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a data-theme=\"light\" data-btn-hover=\"\" href=\"/careers/apprenticeships-training-contracts\" class=\"btn w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg light\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle light\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text light\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Find out more</p></div></a></div></div></div><div class=\"signposts_item\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-0\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Training Contracts</h4><p>We’re focused on organic growth, which is why we look to recruit talented Trainee Solicitors and support them all the way through to qualification and beyond.</p></div></div><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a data-theme=\"light\" data-btn-hover=\"\" href=\"/careers/apprenticeships-training-contracts\" class=\"btn w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg light\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle light\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text light\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Find out more</p></div></a></div></div></div><div class=\"signposts_item\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-0\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Work Experience</h4><p>We run week-long placements throughout the year for students keen to gain real experience in a commercial law firm trusted by high net-worth and business clients for exceptional service and client care.</p></div></div><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a data-theme=\"light\" data-btn-hover=\"\" href=\"/careers/work-experience\" class=\"btn w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg light\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle light\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text light\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Find out more</p></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_contact_contact-2\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"contact_contact-2_component\"><div data-duration-in=\"300\" data-duration-out=\"300\" data-current=\"Tab 1\" data-easing=\"ease\" class=\"contact_contact-2_tabs w-tabs\"><div id=\"w-node-_14a1f155-ed5c-1ab0-9aa6-c1b249c3b2b3-49c3b2a9\" class=\"contact_contact-2_tabs-menu w-tab-menu\"><a data-w-tab=\"Tab 1\" class=\"contact_contact-2_tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link w--current\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h5\">Our values</h3></div><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><p>Our culture is key. We know it’s special. As we continue to grow, we want to keep hold of that. Our values shape how we work, how we treat each other, and how we show up every day. They guide our decisions. They set the standard. They make sure that as we grow, we grow in the right way. <br><br>This is what we expect of ourselves and of each other.<br><br>Be Positive. Be Approachable. Be Supportive. Be Present. Be Yourself.<br>‍</p></div></a><a data-w-tab=\"Tab 2\" class=\"contact_contact-2_tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h5\">Diversity and equal opportunities</h3></div><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><p>Our people are our greatest strength. We’re proud to build a team that reflects different backgrounds, perspectives, and experiences. We’re committed to equal opportunities for everyone. That means creating a working environment where you can thrive, develop, and reach your full potential. <br><br>Free from discrimination. Free from harassment. Supported to be yourself. <br></p></div></a><a data-w-tab=\"Tab 3\" class=\"contact_contact-2_tabs-link w-inline-block w-tab-link\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h5\">Our vision</h3></div><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><p>To be an inspirational organisation: The trusted adviser of choice for commercial and high net-worth clients, renowned for exceptional service, and client care.</p></div></a></div><div id=\"w-node-_14a1f155-ed5c-1ab0-9aa6-c1b249c3b2df-49c3b2a9\" class=\"service_tabs-content w-tab-content\"><div data-w-tab=\"Tab 1\" class=\"contact_contact-2_tab-pane w-tab-pane w--tab-active\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11da3f3ecbc519025c99b_portrait_under_1mb.avif\" alt=\"Group of eight diverse professionals standing indoors in business attire in front of a green moss wall.\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11da3f3ecbc519025c99b_portrait_under_1mb-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11da3f3ecbc519025c99b_portrait_under_1mb-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11da3f3ecbc519025c99b_portrait_under_1mb-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11da3f3ecbc519025c99b_portrait_under_1mb-p-1600.avif 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11da3f3ecbc519025c99b_portrait_under_1mb.avif 1638w\" class=\"image\"></div></div><div data-w-tab=\"Tab 2\" class=\"contact_contact-2_tab-pane w-tab-pane\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11e20ee1280c5a54aa3b5_group2_under_1mb.avif\" alt=\"Group of 16 well-dressed people posing indoors in front of a green moss wall with two orange chairs.\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11e20ee1280c5a54aa3b5_group2_under_1mb-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11e20ee1280c5a54aa3b5_group2_under_1mb-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11e20ee1280c5a54aa3b5_group2_under_1mb-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11e20ee1280c5a54aa3b5_group2_under_1mb-p-1600.avif 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11e20ee1280c5a54aa3b5_group2_under_1mb.avif 1638w\" class=\"image\"></div></div><div data-w-tab=\"Tab 3\" class=\"contact_contact-2_tab-pane w-tab-pane\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11db8c78fa5821f32edbe_group_under_1mb.jpg\" alt=\"Group of 22 people in office setting wearing business attire, standing and smiling at camera.\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11db8c78fa5821f32edbe_group_under_1mb-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11db8c78fa5821f32edbe_group_under_1mb-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11db8c78fa5821f32edbe_group_under_1mb-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69f11db8c78fa5821f32edbe_group_under_1mb.jpg 1308w\" class=\"image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section fade=\"trigger\" id=\"w-node-_962b753c-4ddc-3450-0003-3e8660b5ceba-60b5ceba\" class=\"section_why-us\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"why-us_component\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xlarge\"><h2 data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h1\">Why work with us</h2></div><div class=\"w-layout-grid timeline4_content\"><div id=\"w-node-_209249c2-9afc-4ae2-0c65-d5f43b6a6285-60b5ceba\" class=\"timeline4_progress\"><div class=\"timeline4_fade-overlay-top\"></div><div class=\"timeline4_progress-line\"></div><div class=\"timeline4_line\"></div><div class=\"timeline4_fade-overlay-bottom\"></div><div fade=\"details\" class=\"timeline4_progress-line-cover\"></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_content-right\"><div fade=\"details\" class=\"timeline4_row\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle-wrapper\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle\"></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_item\"><div class=\"max-width-small\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h3\">Time, security, and support.</h3></div><p>We believe time away from work matters. That’s why annual leave starts at 24 days, plus Bank Holidays, and increases with length of service. You’ll also get your birthday off, and an extra day at Christmas so you can properly switch off and spend time where it counts. If you want a little more flexibility, our holiday purchase scheme lets you buy additional leave.<br><br>We support your future too. We offer a competitive pension contribution, enhanced maternity, adoption and paternity schemes, and help with travel to work depending on your role. It’s about giving you security, flexibility, and the right support at every stage of life.</p></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_row\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle-wrapper\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle\"></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_item\"><div class=\"max-width-small\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h3\">Looking after your health.</h3></div><p>Our medical support is practical, accessible, and there when you need it. We offer a Medicash healthcare cash plan to help with everyday health costs, along with free flu jabs and bi annual heart health checks to keep you on track.<br> <br>It’s all part of making sure you feel supported, both in and out of work.</p></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_row\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle-wrapper\"><div class=\"timeline4_circle\"></div></div><div class=\"timeline4_item\"><div class=\"max-width-small\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h3\">A community that cares.</h3></div><p>Life at Moonstone means something. We look after our people and create a place where everyone feels supported and connected. From paid counselling and menopause support to financial wellbeing sessions and holistic therapies, we invest in your overall wellbeing.<br><br>We come together too. Whether it’s our January wellbeing month, our Christmas party or our annual quiz and awards night, we make time to celebrate and strengthen the connections that matter.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"why-us_image_component\"><div id=\"w-node-_962b753c-4ddc-3450-0003-3e8660b5ceda-60b5ceba\" class=\"why-us_image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b3c4e081fcff390a682e_Moonstone_Event_Applause_1920w%20(1).avif\" loading=\"lazy\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.1\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b3c4e081fcff390a682e_Moonstone_Event_Applause_1920w%20(1)-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b3c4e081fcff390a682e_Moonstone_Event_Applause_1920w%20(1)-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b3c4e081fcff390a682e_Moonstone_Event_Applause_1920w%20(1)-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b3c4e081fcff390a682e_Moonstone_Event_Applause_1920w%20(1)-p-1600.avif 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b3c4e081fcff390a682e_Moonstone_Event_Applause_1920w%20(1).avif 1920w\" class=\"image is-parallax\"></div><div id=\"w-node-_962b753c-4ddc-3450-0003-3e8660b5cedc-60b5ceba\" class=\"why-us_image-wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a5b3fd83bef0104ba5483e_Moonstone_Event_Laughter_1920w.avif\" loading=\"lazy\" data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.1\" alt=\"\" class=\"image is-parallax\"></div></div></div></div></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a