ponent\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xxlarge\"><div class=\"insight-hub_event_heading-wrapper\"><div class=\"insight-hub_event_heading\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-xsmall\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2\">More than a workplace</h2></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Work matters. But so do the moments in between.<br></p></div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-type=\"static\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-gallery-slider\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_instance\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_list-wrapper\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_slide\"><div class=\"image-wrapper-3-2\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58e1ee69b3aab366e2fbc_Team_Group_Standing_1920w.avif\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58e1ee69b3aab366e2fbc_Team_Group_Standing_1920w-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58e1ee69b3aab366e2fbc_Team_Group_Standing_1920w-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58e1ee69b3aab366e2fbc_Team_Group_Standing_1920w-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58e1ee69b3aab366e2fbc_Team_Group_Standing_1920w-p-1600.avif 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58e1ee69b3aab366e2fbc_Team_Group_Standing_1920w.avif 1920w\" class=\"image-wrapper_image\"></div><div class=\"margin-top margin-xsmall\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h5\">This Is Us - An opportunity for our teams to share what they do, helping everyone at Moonstone better understand and connect with the people behind each practice area.</h3></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_slide\"><div class=\"image-wrapper-3-2\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.