 proud to sponsor and take part in Kampala Pride, championing a culture where individuality is valued and everyone feels they belong.</h3></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_slide\"><div class=\"image-wrapper-3-2\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f2bc48346ca0f8a186f_Team_Group_Photo_1920w.jpg\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f2bc48346ca0f8a186f_Team_Group_Photo_1920w-p-500.jpg 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f2bc48346ca0f8a186f_Team_Group_Photo_1920w-p-800.jpg 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f2bc48346ca0f8a186f_Team_Group_Photo_1920w-p-1080.jpg 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f2bc48346ca0f8a186f_Team_Group_Photo_1920w-p-1600.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f2bc48346ca0f8a186f_Team_Group_Photo_1920w.jpg 1920w\" class=\"image-wrapper_image\"></div><div class=\"margin-top margin-xsmall\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h5\">This Is Me - A lunch time session where our people share their journeys, challenges, achievements and what truly matters to them, because everyone&#x27;s story deserves to be heard.</h3></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_slide\"><div class=\"image-wrapper-3-2\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f797908e510af50ef6e_Halloween_Bake_Sale_1920w%20(1).avif\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f797908e510af50ef6e_Halloween_Bake_Sale_1920w%20(1)-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f797908e510af50ef6e_Halloween_Bake_Sale_1920w%20(1)-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f797908e510af50ef6e_Halloween_Bake_Sale_1920w%20(1)-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f797908e510af50ef6e_Halloween_Bake_Sale_1920w%20(1)-p-1600.avif 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58f797908e510af50ef6e_Halloween_Bake_Sale_1920w%20(1).avif 1920w\" class=\"image-wrapper_image\"></div><div class=\"margin-top margin-xsmall\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h5\">Charity Bake Sales - Throughout the year, our teams roll up their sleeves (and icing bags) to raise money for our Charity of the Year.</h3></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_slide\"><div class=\"image-wrapper-3-2\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58fb4808bfae227e767d0_Team_Dragon_Boat_1920w.avif\" alt=\"\" sizes=\"100vw\" srcset=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58fb4808bfae227e767d0_Team_Dragon_Boat_1920w-p-500.avif 500w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58fb4808bfae227e767d0_Team_Dragon_Boat_1920w-p-800.avif 800w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58fb4808bfae227e767d0_Team_Dragon_Boat_1920w-p-1080.avif 1080w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58fb4808bfae227e767d0_Team_Dragon_Boat_1920w-p-1600.avif 1600w, https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69a58fb4808bfae227e767d0_Team_Dragon_Boat_1920w.avif 1920w\" class=\"image-wrapper_image\"></div><div class=\"margin-top margin-xsmall\"><h3 class=\"heading-style-h5\">Dragon Boat Race - A firm favourite that brings out our teamwork, resilience and a healthy dose of competitive fun.</h3></div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-gallery-slider_navigation\"><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"ht